{"tid":98333,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"感謝你送一份難忘既生日禮物比我","createTime":"2017-01-28T10:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T21:16:11.000Z","uid":17210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34aa02e5c05f856180caed059f8005f07dfb6188","tid":98333,"uid":17210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"你簡人 人簡你<br />\n<br />\n你選擇左唔簡我<br />\n<br />\n原諒我祝福唔到你地<br />\n<br />\n我真係好唔開心好難過每一晚都失眠<br />\n<br />\n你話我講野令你難受，我一定會去改<br />\n<br />\n曾經為你付出既野希望你會記得<br />\n<br />\n希望你唔會睇到，就算睇到都唔好去估依個係咪我<br />\n<br />\n多謝你有提前去同我慶祝生日，我好滿足<br />\n<br />\n當日送完你我另轉身就已經喊緊<br />\n<br />\n對唔住，多謝你"},{"pid":"239ea60e2e872366ebf6bbd7667c5a756f4dd63c","tid":98333,"uid":17210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2f27f0b6123660b7724711ff1a20526bba973a","tid":98333,"uid":17210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97af4498cd0ce168646254e0b48e8e46768245f3","tid":98333,"uid":20859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 振作"},{"pid":"6afe01da4efdeac86cd7adf754063ae09ec0997d","tid":98333,"uid":17210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T13:18:27.000Z","msg":"本應今日生日係應該開心<br />\n<br />\n但我開心唔到"},{"pid":"1962fa77b581b8648021bba3b8e5f3c36ce67420","tid":98333,"uid":17210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ea5cfa3b9562c1fc1968ffe181b5f87f1370b2","tid":98333,"uid":76942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:51:36.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"